@startuml fig-tls-handshake
skinparam backgroundColor white
skinparam defaultFontName Arial
skinparam defaultFontSize 11
skinparam shadowing false
title Handshake TLS 1.3 (1-RTT)

participant "Client" as C
participant "Server" as S

C -> S : ClientHello\n+ suite cifrare + partajare cheie
S --> C : ServerHello + partajare cheie\n+ Certificat + Finished
C -> S : Finished

== Date Aplicatie Criptate ==
C <-> S : Trafic HTTPS

legend right
TLS 1.3: 1-RTT (vs 2-RTT in 1.2)
Reluare 0-RTT cu PSK
Secretul forward obligatoriu
AES_256_GCM_SHA384
endlegend
@enduml
